                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2787" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0192</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10397 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“龙虎斗”之破局：斐克公司双主营业务之冲突管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">裴利芳，姬东伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京市斐克科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">VR技术创新；仿真软件；龙虎斗；冲突；冲突管理；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">VR Technology Innovation;  Simulation Software;  The Conflict between &quot;Dragon and Tiger&quot;;  Conflict；Conflict  Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京市斐克科技有限责任公司（以下简称“斐克公司”）专注于培训擅长使用先进制造设备的高技能人才。本案例讲述了斐克公司为促进技术培训业务的发展，通过VR技术创新开创出了仿真软件业务，使公司呈现出双主营业务并存的情形。随着软件的升级完善，两个原本可相互促进的主营业务部门之间却出现了诸多困扰高层的“争斗”现象，最后连两部门的主管副总也涉身其中，拉开了“龙虎斗”之大戏。对此，如何破局就成了关乎公司未来的大事。本案例通过还原真实场景，旨在引导学员运用冲突管理相关理论全面完整地分析 “龙虎斗”冲突的背景、根源、过程及相关解决策略。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Beijing Phic technology co.,ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot; Phic &quot;) specialized in training high skilled personnel who can use advanced manufacturing equipment. This case tells Phic in order to promote the development of technical training services, through the VR technology innovation to create a simulation software business, established in double main business coexist situation. Along with the successful development of the simulation software, two originally mutual promotion of the main business department appeared one after another by the senior management of the &quot;struggle&quot; phenomenon, and finally even the two department director also involved, resulting in the conflict between &quot;Dragon and Tiger&quot; situation. In the face of this dilemma, how breaking it has become a top priority for the future development of the Phic. In this case enterprise through the reduction of the real scene, to guide the students to comprehensively use the theory of knowledge management to complete conflict analysis, thinking of the conflict between &quot;Dragon and Tiger&quot; in the background, causes, process and related solutions. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冲突分类模型；组织中的冲突层次；冲突过程；托马斯冲突二维模式；冲突强度的连续体；领导方格模型；合作式冲突解决模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-08</td>
                            </tr>
